    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Whew..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sir Julio?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Sophie. What a coincidence."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes. What are you doing here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I was running as part of my training."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Running?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "A knight's greatest asset is his body. It's important to train like this every day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Wow, every day...? That sounds really hard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, true, it was difficult at first. I wouldn't even be able to move after a day of training with the knights."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "You had a time like that...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "But it's training like that which creates a knight who can truly protect others."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You also need a lot of strength to swing around a greatsword."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "With that in mind, I trained hard, and eventually my body grew stronger. It's no longer as difficult as it was before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I see... But it still sounds like a lot of work..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "...Oh dear, I spent too much time resting. I'll return to my training now. See you again, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry for interrupting you. Do your best with your training!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Thank you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "It's amazing that he works so hard every day..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Alright, I need to work harder at my alchemy!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Julio learned the skill \"<CLGR>Steel Spirit<CLNR>\"."
        }
    ]
}